org.apache.flex.swf.tags

Interface IManagedTag

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefineSceneAndFrameLabelDataTag, EnableDebugger2Tag, EndTag, ExportAssetsTag, FileAttributesTag, FrameLabelTag, MetadataTag, ProductInfoTag, ScriptLimitsTag, SetBackgroundColorTag, ShowFrameTag, SymbolClassTag

    public interface IManagedTag
    A "managed" SWF tag cannot be added to SWFFrame pragmatically. It is managed by the frame internally.

    For example, SymbolClass and ShowFrame are managed tags.
